{"tid":1813381,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"破欠基金3000宗申請 建造業佔三分一","createTime":"2020-01-06T08:38:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T10:00:57.000Z","uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d756c920cd0218f3032bd16a98935275e2efc2a1","tid":1813381,"uid":185631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"破欠基金3000宗申請 建造業佔三分一<br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】財政司長陳茂波昨在網誌表示，很多中小企正面對經營困難，破產欠薪保障基金於過去一年錄得近3000宗申請，以建造業佔最多，達1158宗，佔整體申請逾三分一。陳茂波又表示，由按揭證券公司推出的「九成信貸擔保產品」自本月16日接受申請後，短短一星期銀行已收到數十宗申請（詳見B4）。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波稱，過去12個月內破欠基金接獲近3000宗申請，申請最多的5個行業，分別為建造業（1158宗）、餐飲服務（716宗）、零售業（233宗）、進出口貿易（220宗）及其他個人服務活動（80宗）。他說，很多企業正咬緊牙關、吃力經營，盼望社會氣氛緩和，暴力停止。陳茂波擔心若市况未能迅速改善，新年後將可能出現結業潮。<br />\n<br />\n業界：申請者多二判三判<br />\n香港建造商會行政總裁謝子華表示，申請破欠基金的建造公司，絕大部分是分包商，即俗稱的二判、三判等。部分於過去1年面臨周轉不靈或管理欠佳，面對工人追討薪金只能申請破產。<br />\n<br />\n謝子華稱，過去5年建造業面對立法會拉布以及近期社會事件影響下，業界對前景缺乏信心，促政府更多支援，包括為建造業設立專項信貸保證業金，以改善建造業公司的現金周轉，以及豁免房委會名冊登記費等。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191223/s00002/1577039223377/%E7%A0%B4%E6%AC%A0%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%913000%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191223%2Fs00002%2F1577039223377%2F%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%25913000%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDSIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=37ac59da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20191223%2Fs00002%2F1577039223377%2F%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E5%259F%25BA%25E9%2587%25913000%25E5%25AE%2597%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B-%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E4%25BD%2594%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%2588%2586%25E4%25B8%2580&h=81f100b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20191223/s00002/1577039223377/%E7%A0%B4%E6%AC%A0%E5%9F%BA%E9%87%913000%E5%AE%97%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B-%E5%BB%BA%E9%80%A0%E6%A5%AD%E4%BD%94%E4%B8%89%E5%88%86%E4%B8%80</a>"},{"pid":"a3630d43491ba69251e1c1be577b5536537e5cc6","tid":1813381,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:39:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be4e404aad50062ab3812717eef87ceb37b03e31","tid":1813381,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:40:19.000Z","msg":"【第貳拾期牆紙】 破局<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1804841/page/1</a><br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDSIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=2cf99de6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aypmVes.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaypmVes.jpg&h=462652b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbb14b8badc2b7fa8f49872d13d6c3b649910c39","tid":1813381,"uid":81273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:57:29.000Z","msg":"賤種藍絲又走數"},{"pid":"381884f88cb81dec90cb93ab52b8e6c5df30af0e","tid":1813381,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:57:34.000Z","msg":"遲啲仲多呀，政府cut 晒大學啲工程<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38635298be332546f252a70b56d983b90bc8e4bc","tid":1813381,"uid":89514,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd6f39e0a62674f9a465b284ed23a4e013e980b","tid":1813381,"uid":284855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T09:01:23.000Z","msg":"轉資破產走人工數， fatfat<img src=\"/assets/f